{Songs:[{Guid:"57/aeob2MEWGwIAG0G2Hdw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
Isaia 22: 19-23</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GÜTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RiA MÜRATHI ISAIA</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani akimenyithia Shebna üü : Atiriri, ngagütugutania urutwo wira-ini waku, uguthwo uru two handü haku hau hatüügiru .</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Na ni gügakinya atiri, müthenya ücio,ati ni ngeta ndungata yakwa Eliakim wa Hilikia, ndimühumbe nguo yaku iria ndaya, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndimühotore mwihotoro waku, na wira wa ku wa gwathana ndiwikire moko-ini make ; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ücio niwe ügatuika ta ithe wa andü aria matüüraga Jerusalemu, na wa andü a nyümba ya Juda. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kihingüro kia nyümba ya Davide-ri, ngakiigirira kiande - ini giake, atuike mühingüraniri, na gütigie mühinganiriria ; na ahinganagiririe na gütigie mühinguraniri o na atü;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na ndimuoherere handü harümu aikare ho ta mücumari ühüriirüo handü, atuike ogiti  gia üthamaki kii riri thiini wa nyümba ya ithe.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani .</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GÜCOKERÜO
Thaburi 138: 1-2a; 2b-3; 6 na 8</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : </s></f><i><fArial Black><s2769>Küringana na ütugi waku, Mwathani, ndümütiganiria</s></f></i><fArial Black><s2769>.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ni ngügücokeria ngatho na ngoro yakwa yothe, ngüküinira ngukugoocaga ngai ciothe iri o ho. Ngüinamirira njerekeire hekarü yaku theru.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<i><fArial Black><s2769>Küringana na ütugi waku, Mwathani, ndümütiganiria.</s></f></i>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Njokerie ritwa riaku ngatho ni ündü wa ütugi waku, na tondü wa wihokeku waku o naguo, amu nikünenehia ünenehetie uuge waku küri maündü maria mangi ma ritwa riaku mothe.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Müthio üria ndetanire, wee ni wanyamukiirie; ni wanyümiriirie ni künjikira
 hinya ngoro.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<i><fArial Black><s2769>Küringana na ütugi waku, Mwathani, ndümütiganiria.</s></f></i>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ni hindü, o na gwatuika Mwathani e igürü müno, ni aroraga mündü mühoreri;indi, uria mwitüügiria, akamümenyera o küraya. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani, maündü makwa ni akamakindira: ütugi waku, Mwathani, ni wa tene na tene; wira wa moko maku-ri, ndükanaütiganirie.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<i><fArial Black><s2769>Küringana na ütugi waku, Mwathani, ndümütiganiria</s></f></i><fArial Black><s2769>.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GiTHOMO KiA IGIRT	
Aroma 11 : 33-36</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GÜTHOMA MARÜA MA MÜTHURE PAUL KÜRi ANDÜ A ROMA</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>i üügi wa Ngai, o naguo umenyi wake-ri, matikiri maingi na mariku ! Matuiro make, kai matingica rika gitümi kiamo;</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> migendere yake nayo, kai ndingituirika -i ! Amu ni mündü ürikü Wanamenya meciria ma Mwathani ? kana ni ürikü wanatuika wa ndundu yake ? Kana riri, nü wanaamba kü.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> mühe kindü, nake akarihwo kindü kiu ? Amu-ri, maündü mothe no hari we moimire,na gütüürio matüüragio no we,</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na no küri we merekeire. Nake arogoocagwo tene na tene. Ni gutuike guo.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RÜiMBO RüA INJIRI	
Mathayo 16, 18
Alleluya, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Wee niwe Petro, na igürü ria ndümba ya ihiga riri ni ngaaka Kanitha wakwa, na ihingo cia kwa ngoma itikaütoria.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Alleluya .</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GiTHOMO KIA INJIRI	Mathayo 16; 13-20</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GiCUNJi KIA INJIRI THERU TA ÜRiA YANDiKiTWO Ni MÜTHURE MATHAYO</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi iyo Yesu aakinya bürüri-ini wa Cesarea wa Filippo, akiüria arutwo ake atiri : Andü moigaga ati Mürü wa mündü nüü? </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao makiuga atiri: Amwe moigaga ati niwe John Mübatithania; na amwe makoiga niwe Elia ; na angi makoiga niwe Jeremia, kana ümwe waarathi.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Nake akimoria : Inyui na inyui muugaga ni nii üü? Nake Simone Petro akimücokeria akimwira atiri: Wee, niwe Kristu, Mürü wa Ngai üria wi muoyo.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Nake Yesu akimücokeria akimwira : Gükena-ri, niwe Simone, mürü wa Jona : ni ündü ti mündü wi mwiri na thakame üküguüriirie üguo, no ni Awa üria wi igüru.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Na ningükwira atiri. Wee niwe Petro, o na igürü ria ndümba ya ihiga riri ni ngaaka Kanitha wakwa: o na ihingo cia kwa ngoma itikaütoria.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ni ngakühe ihingüro cia üthamaki wa lgürü : na kiria o giothe ükoha gükü thi ni gikohwo lgürü; na kiria o giothe ükohora gükü thi, ni gikohorüo Igürü.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Hindi io agikaania arutwo ake matikae kwira mündü o na ümwe ati niwe Kristü .</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJIRI YA MWATHANI</s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA KIMWE MWAKA A"},{Guid:"PRn0tnjmz0CElTMz4+8hiA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA INYA MWAKA A</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA MBERE	
Sirach 27: 30 - 28: 7</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GÜTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA SIRACH</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Urakari na wirihiria,ni maündü moru, namo meeri makoragwo na mündü mwihia. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uria wothe wendaga kwirihiria, ni arimenyaga wirihiria wa Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>üria üririkanaga mawihia ma mündü.
Kiririria mündü üria üngi ihitia riria </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agwikite, na riria ükühoya, ni üriohagirüo mehia maku. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mündi angikorüo ni aigaga marakara na mündü üria üngi-ri, akihota gweterera ükiririria kuuma küri </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani? I angikiaga küigwira mündü take tha-ri, akihota gükiriririo mehia make wee </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akiri mündi üria üigaga marakara ngoro-ini yake - ri: nüü üngikimükiririria mawihia make ?</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ririkana maündü ma ürigia na tiga güthürana, ririkana übuthu na ikua na urümagie mawathi. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ririkana mawathi na ndügaikare üri na muku na mündü o ürikü;</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makiria ririkana kirikaniro kia uria Uri-lgürü ma, na üriganirüo ni mahitia maria wikitwo.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GÜCOKERÜO
Thaburi 103: 1-2; 3-4; 9-10; 11.12 </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani ni wa matha maingi na ni muuma andü müno.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>l. Ngoro yakwa, gatha Mwathani; gwata kiria o giothe thiini wakwa nikigathe ritwa riake riamüre.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngoro yakwa, kigathe Mwathani, na ndukariganiruo ni wega o na ümwe maria agwikaga</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani ni wa matha maingi na ni muuma andü müno.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Ari we ükuohagira waganu waku wothe, ndüari ciaku ciothe o nacio nowe mukuhonia;</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we muküüri muoyo waku hari irima ria gikuü, na nowe mügwiki maündü </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ma ütugi na ma matha maigü, ta ari thumbi aragwikira ya unene.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani ni wa matha maingi na ni muuma andü müno.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Ndangiikara o acirithanagia hindi ciothe, na ndangitüüra arakarite nginya tene na tene. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndatwikite ta üria mahitia maitü maagiriirüo, kana agatücokeria küringana na üria waganu witü üigana .</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani ni wa matha maingi na ni muuma andü müno.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4.Ni amu, oguo matu-ini kühacite o igürü ria thi, no taguo ütugi wake üneneheire aria amwitigiri.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O ta aria irathiro küraihaniriirie na ithüiro, no taguo atüthengeirie mehia maitu matüraihiririe .</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani ni wa matha maingi na ni muuma andü müno.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGIRl	
Aroma 14 : 7- 9</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GÚTHOMA MARÜA MA MÜTHURE PAUL KURI ANDU A ROMA</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aruna aitü, ithui-ri , gütiri mündu o na umwe utuuraga no ündü wake wiki,</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na gükua gütiri ükuaga no ündü wake wiki. </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni ündü tungikoruo tugutuura muoyo, twatüüra türi a Mwathani ;</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tüngikorüo tükuite, twakua türi o ro a Mwathani tondu ucio-ri o na küngituika ni riu türi muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana riria tüngikorüo tükuite - ri , türi o a mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Amu ühoro üyü níguo watümire Kristü akue na acoke muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ati niguo atuike Mwathani o wa aria maanakua na wa aria mari muoyo .</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kiugo cia Mwathani .</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RÜIMBO RÜA INJIRI	
John 13; 34</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya. </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani akuuga üü : Ngümühe riathani rieru ni ati mwendane, 
o ta üguo nii ndimwendete .</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Alleluya .</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI	
Mathayo 18 : 21 -35</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJIRI THERU TA URIA YANDIKITWO NI MUTHURE MATHAYO</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi io Petro agiüka kuri Yesu akimuuria atiri : </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani, muru wa Awa anginjihia manjihia maigana ngimuohagira? </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni maita mugwanja? Yesu akimwira atirii: Ndigükwira ati, no kinya maita mügwanja; </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no riri, kaba mirongo mugwanja maita mugwanja.Ni ündu ücio üthamaki wa lgürü </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni wa kühaananio na müthamaki muna uria wendaga kuheo uhoro wa mbia ciake ni ngombo ciake.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na aambiriria kwiruo ühoro ucio, ngombo imwe yari na thiri wake wa taranda ngiri ikümi .</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na tondü ni yaremetwo ni küriha, mwathani wayo agiathana ati yendio, yo nyene na mütumia wayo,</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ciana, o na indo ciayo ciothe, ni getha thiri ürihike. Ni ündü ücio ngombo io ikiigüithia thi ikimüthaitha,</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikimwiraga atiri: Mwathani, tiga güthethükira na ni ngaküriha wothe. Na mwathani wa ngombo io </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akiringwo ni tha, akimiohera, akimirekera thiri ücio.
No riri, ngombo io ikiumagara </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikiona ngombo ingi yarutaga wira nayo, na yari </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na thiri wayo wa ciringi igana rimwe :nayo ikimukumbata, ikiminyita mümero, ikimwira atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndiha thiri wakwa. Ni ündü wa üguo ngombo io yarutaga wira nayo ikiigüithia thi ikimuthaitha, : </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tiga guthethükira na ni ngaküriha. Nayo ikirega , igithii, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikimiikithia korokoro-ini, o nginya riria ikariha thiri ücio.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na riria ngombo iria ingi ciarutaga wira nayo cionire üria gwekirüo,igikiigua kieha müno, ikiira </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwathani wacio ühoro ücio wothe.
Hindi io mwathani wayo akimita akimira atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee ngombo ino njaganu, ngürekeire thiri ücio wothe,</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni ündü ni üthaithire:
githi ndükwagiriirüo o nawe ni </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>küiguira tha ngombo iria mürutaga wira nayo,o ta üguo nii na nii ngüiguiriire tha? </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake mwathani wayo akirakara, akimineana kwi aherithania </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikohwo o nginya riria ikariha thiri ucio wothe. Uguo </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>noguo Awa uria wi iguru akamwika inyui , </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mungiaga kuohanagira na ma o mundu na muru wa ithe.</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>injiri ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
