Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : Mwathani ni wa matha maingi na ni muuma andü müno.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA IGIRl	
Aroma 14 : 7- 9</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GÚTHOMA MARÜA MA MÜTHURE PAUL KURI ANDU A ROMA</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aruna aitü, ithui-ri , gütiri mündu o na umwe utuuraga no ündü wake wiki,</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na gükua gütiri ükuaga no ündü wake wiki. </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ündü tungikoruo tugutuura muoyo, twatüüra türi a Mwathani ;</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na tüngikorüo tükuite, twakua türi o ro a Mwathani tondu ucio-ri o na küngituika ni riu türi muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na kana riria tüngikorüo tükuite - ri , türi o a mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Amu ühoro üyü níguo watümire Kristü akue na acoke muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ati niguo atuike Mwathani o wa aria maanakua na wa aria mari muoyo .</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kiugo cia Mwathani .</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RÜIMBO RÜA INJIRI	
John 13; 34</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya, Alleluya. </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani akuuga üü : Ngümühe riathani rieru ni ati mwendane, 
o ta üguo nii ndimwendete .</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Alleluya .</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI	
Mathayo 18 : 21 -35</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJIRI THERU TA URIA YANDIKITWO NI MUTHURE MATHAYO</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi io Petro agiüka kuri Yesu akimuuria atiri : </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani, muru wa Awa anginjihia manjihia maigana ngimuohagira? </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni maita mugwanja? Yesu akimwira atirii: Ndigükwira ati, no kinya maita mügwanja; </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>no riri, kaba mirongo mugwanja maita mugwanja.Ni ündu ücio üthamaki wa lgürü </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni wa kühaananio na müthamaki muna uria wendaga kuheo uhoro wa mbia ciake ni ngombo ciake.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na aambiriria kwiruo ühoro ucio, ngombo imwe yari na thiri wake wa taranda ngiri ikümi .</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na tondü ni yaremetwo ni küriha, mwathani wayo agiathana ati yendio, yo nyene na mütumia wayo,</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ciana, o na indo ciayo ciothe, ni getha thiri ürihike. Ni ündü ücio ngombo io ikiigüithia thi ikimüthaitha,</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikimwiraga atiri: Mwathani, tiga güthethükira na ni ngaküriha wothe. Na mwathani wa ngombo io </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akiringwo ni tha, akimiohera, akimirekera thiri ücio.
No riri, ngombo io ikiumagara </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikiona ngombo ingi yarutaga wira nayo, na yari </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na thiri wayo wa ciringi igana rimwe :nayo ikimukumbata, ikiminyita mümero, ikimwira atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndiha thiri wakwa. Ni ündü wa üguo ngombo io yarutaga wira nayo ikiigüithia thi ikimuthaitha, : </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tiga guthethükira na ni ngaküriha. Nayo ikirega , igithii, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikimiikithia korokoro-ini, o nginya riria ikariha thiri ücio.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na riria ngombo iria ingi ciarutaga wira nayo cionire üria gwekirüo,igikiigua kieha müno, ikiira </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwathani wacio ühoro ücio wothe.
Hindi io mwathani wayo akimita akimira atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee ngombo ino njaganu, ngürekeire thiri ücio wothe,</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni ündü ni üthaithire:
githi ndükwagiriirüo o nawe ni </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>küiguira tha ngombo iria mürutaga wira nayo,o ta üguo nii na nii ngüiguiriire tha? </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake mwathani wayo akirakara, akimineana kwi aherithania </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikohwo o nginya riria ikariha thiri ucio wothe. Uguo </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>noguo Awa uria wi iguru akamwika inyui , </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mungiaga kuohanagira na ma o mundu na muru wa ithe.</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>injiri ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA INYA MWAKA A
"},{Guid:"dPWOKdT/zUSP8zX0HHK02Q",Verses:[{ID:21,
Text:"INJILI            Mathayo 14:22-33"},{ID:22,
Text:"{Baada ya watu wote kushiba,} Yesu aliwahimiza wafuasi wake"},{ID:23,
Text:"Wapande mashua na kumtangulia kufika hadi ıng'ambo,
yeye  akiwaaga watu."},{ID:23,
Text:"Baada ya kuwaaga watu, alipanda mlimani peke yake kusali. "},{ID:24,
Text:"Kukawa jioni, naye alikuwako huko peke yake."},{ID:24,
Text:"Wakati huo chombo kilikuwa maili kadhaa mbali na pwani, "},{ID:25,
Text:"kikisongwa na mawimbi, kwa maana upepo ulikipiga."},{ID:25,
Text:"Wakati wa zamu ya nne ya usiku, aliwakaribia akitembea juu ya bahari. "},{ID:26,
Text:"Wafuasi walipomwona anatembea baharini, walifadhaika, wakasema, \"Ni kivuli.\" "},{ID:26,
Text:"Wakapiga yowe kwa hofu. Mara Yesu akawaambia, \"Tulieni, ni mimi msiogope.\""},{ID:27,
Text:"Petro akamjibu, akasema,\"Bwana, ikiwa ni wewe, niamuru nije kwako juu ya maji.\""},{ID:27,
Text:"Naye akasema, \"Njoo.\"Petro akashuka mashuani, akamjonge"},{ID:28,
Text:"Yesu akitembea juu ya maji. 
Lakini alipoona uvumi wa upepo, aliogopa, "},{ID:29,
Text:"akaanza kuzama. Akapiga yowe, akaita, \"Bwana, uniokoe.\""},{ID:28,
Text:"Mara Yesu akanyosha mkono, akamshika, akamwambia,"},{ID:29,
Text:" \"Ewe mwenye imani haba,
 mbona uliona shaka?\" "},{ID:30,
Text:"Nao walipopanda chomboni, upepo ulitulia."},{ID:29,
Text:"Watu waliokuwa chomboni wakamsujudia, wakisema, "},{ID:30,
Text:"\"Hakika, wewe u Mwana wa Mungu.\""},{ID:30,
Text:"Injili ya Bwana."}],
Text:"DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA TISA MWAKA A"},{Guid:"Gf7hAxH14k2SPfBvkiy98Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA SITA MWAKA A</s></f></b>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA</s></f></b>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1846>Hakuna mungu mwingine ila wewe, ambaye unavijali vitu </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Vyote hata utakiwe kumwonyesha kwamba hukuhukumu pasipo haki. </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1846>maana, nguvu zako ni chanzo cha haki; na utawala </s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wako juu ya vyote unakufanya uwe ukivihurumia vyote.</s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1846>Naam, huwaonyesha nguvu wasiouamini uwezo wako na </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuulaumu ujasiri wao waujuao. Lakini wewe, mtawala nguvu, unahukumu kwa </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1846>upole, na kutuongoza kwa huruma nyingi. maana uwezo unao wa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kutenda utakalo wakati wowote. Kwa njia ya kutenda hivyo, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1846>uliwafundisha watu wako, kwamba mtu mwenye haki lazima </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>awe mpenda watu; nawe ukawafanya watoto wako kuwa na tumaini </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1846>njema, kwa sababu huwajalia kutubu juu ya dhambi zao. 
</s></f><b><fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f></b>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384></s><b><fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZA</s></f></b>"},{ID:8,Style:{Body:{FontSize:204}},
Text:"<s1384></s><b><u><fArial Black><s1384>KIITIKIO
</s></f></u></b><b><fArial Black><s1384>Wewe, ee Bwana, ni mwema na mwenye huruma</s></f></b>"},{ID:9,Style:{Body:{FontSize:204}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Wewe, ee Bwana, ni mwema na mpole, umejaa </s></f>"},{ID:10,Style:{Body:{FontSize:204}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>huruma kwa wote wanaokuomba.</s></f>"},{ID:11,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Usikie, ee Bwana, sala yangu; uielekee sauti ya maombi yangu. </s></f>"},{ID:10,Style:{Body:{FontSize:214}},
Text:"<s1384></s><b><fArial Black><s1384>Wewe, ee Bwana, ni mwema na mwenye huruma</s></f></b>"},{ID:11,Style:{Body:{FontSize:214}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Mataifa yote uliyofanya watakuja, ee Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:12,Style:{Body:{FontSize:214}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>watakuabudu wewe, watalitukuza jina lako.</s></f>"},{ID:13,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>kwani wewe ni mkuu na mfanya miujiza; ndiwe Mungu peke yako. </s></f>"},{ID:12,Style:{Body:{FontSize:244}},
Text:"<s1384></s><b><fArial Black><s1384>Wewe, ee Bwana, ni mwema na mwenye huruma</s></f></b>"},{ID:13,Style:{Body:{FontSize:244}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Lakini wewe, ee Bwana, ni Mungu mwenye huruma na mpole, </s></f>"},{ID:14,Style:{Body:{FontSize:234}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>mvumilivu, mwenye wema na uaminifu mwingi. unielekezee macho, unihurumie</s></f>"},{ID:14,Style:{Body:{FontSize:244}},
Text:"<s1384></s><b><fArial Black><s1384>Wewe, ee Bwana, ni mwema na mwenye huruma</s></f></b>"},{ID:15,Style:{Body:{FontSize:264}},
Text:"<s1384></s><b><fArial Black><s1384>SOMO LA PILI 
Warumi 8:26-27</s></f></b>"},{ID:16,Style:{Body:{FontSize:196}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Ndugu zangu:
Roho anasaidia udhaifu wetu. Hatujui jinsi inavyotubidi </s></f>"},{ID:17,Style:{Body:{FontSize:244}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>kuomba. Roho mwenyewe anatuombea sisi kwa maombi yasiyosemeka.</s></f>"},{ID:18,Style:{Body:{FontSize:244}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Lakini Mungu achunguzaye mioyo ajua nia ya Roho 
anayewaombea watakatifu kwa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:19,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1384>Neno Ia Bwana.</s></f></b>"},{ID:20,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<s1384></s><b><u><fArial Black><s1384>SHANGILIO LA INJILI</s></f></u></b>"},{ID:21,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Nakushukuru, Baba, Bwana wa mbingu na dunia, </s></f>"},{ID:22,Style:{Body:{FontSize:194}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>kwa kuwa umewafunulia watoto wadogo mafumbo ya ufalme. </s></f>"},{ID:21,Style:{Body:{FontSize:254}},
Text:"<s1384></s><b><u><fArial Black><s1384>INJILI</s></f></u></b><b><fArial Black><s1384>  
Mathayo 13:24-43 </s></f></b>"},{ID:22,Style:{Body:{FontSize:224}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Wakati ule:
Yesu aliwasimulia mfano mwingine akisema, \"Ufalme wa mbingu </s></f>"},{ID:23,Style:{Body:{FontSize:224}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>umefanana na mtu aliyepanda mbegu njema katika shamba lake. </s></f>"},{ID:24,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Lakini watu walipolala usingizi, adui yake akaja, akapanda </s></f>"},{ID:24,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>magugu kati ya ngano, akaenda zake.</s></f>"},{ID:25,Style:{Body:{FontSize:196}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Miche ilipomea na kuchanua, magugu pia yakaonekana.</s></f>"},{ID:25,Style:{Body:{FontSize:196}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Hapo watumishi wa mwenye shamba wakamwendea na kumwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:26,Style:{Body:{FontSize:180}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>'Bwana, hukupanda mbegu njema katika shamba </s></f>"},{ID:26,Style:{Body:{FontSize:196}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>lako? Basi limepataje magugu ? '
 Akawaambia, 'Adui amefanya haya.</s></f>"},{ID:27,Style:{Body:{FontSize:196}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>watumishi wakamwuliza, 'Je, wataka twende kuyakusanya Akasema, </s></f>"},{ID:28,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>'La, sivyo, msije mkang'oa ngano pamoja na magugu </s></f>"},{ID:28,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>mnayotaka kukusanya. Acheni mbegu zote mbili zikue </s></f>"},{ID:29,Style:{Body:{FontSize:180}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>pamoja mpaka wakati wa mavuno. Na wakati wa mavuno nitawaambia </s></f>"},{ID:29,Style:{Body:{FontSize:180}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>wavunaji, \"Kusanyeni kwanza magugu, mkayafunge matita matita na </s></f>"},{ID:30,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>kuyachoma moto. Na kisha hapo kusanyeni ngano ghalani mwangu.</s></f>"},{ID:30,Style:{Body:{FontSize:244}},
Text:"<s1384></s><b><fArial Black><s1384>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f></b>"},{ID:31,Style:{Body:{FontSize:188}},
Text:"<s1384></s><b><fArial Black><s1384>{INJILI NDEFU}</s></f></b>"},{ID:32,Style:{Body:{FontSize:188}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Wakati ule:
Yesu aliwasimulia mfano mwingine akisema, \"Ufalme wa mbingu </s></f>"},{ID:33,Style:{Body:{FontSize:188}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>umefanana na mtu aliyepanda mbegu njema katika shamba lake. </s></f>"},{ID:34,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Lakini watu walipolala usingizi, adui yake akaja' akapanda magugu </s></f>"},{ID:34,Style:{Body:{FontSize:180}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>kati ya ngano, akaenda zake.
Miche ilipomea na kuchanua, magugu pia yakaonekana.</s></f>"},{ID:35,Style:{Body:{FontSize:164}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Hapo watumishi wa mwenye shamba wakamwendea
na kumwambia, 'Bwana, hukupanda mbegu njema katika shamba </s></f>"},{ID:36,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>lako? Basi limepataje magugu ? '
Akawaambia, 'Adui amefanya haya.' Watumishi wakamwuliza 'Je, </s></f>"},{ID:37,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>wataka twende tukayakusanye?' Akasema, 'La, sivyo, </s></f>"},{ID:38,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>msije mkang'oa ngano pamoja na magugu mnayotaka kukusanya.</s></f>"},{ID:38,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Acheni mbegu zote mbili zikue pamoja mpaka wakati wa mavuno. </s></f>"},{ID:39,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Na wakati wa mavuno nitawaambia wavunaji, \"Kusanyeni kwanza </s></f>"},{ID:39,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>magugu, mkayafunge matita matita na kuyachoma moto. </s></f>"},{ID:40,Style:{Body:{FontSize:164}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Na kisha hapo kusanyeni ngano ghalani mwangu. \"'</s></f>"},{ID:40,Style:{Body:{FontSize:164}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Akawasimulia mfano mwingine akisema, 
\"Ufalme wa mbingu umefanana na mbegu ya haradali, </s></f>"},{ID:41,Style:{Body:{FontSize:164}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>aliyoitwaa mtu akaipanda katika 
shamba lake. Nayo ni ndogo kuliko mbegu zote. </s></f>"},{ID:42,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Lakini ikiisha kumea huwa kubwa kuliko mboga zote, 
ikawa mti, hata ndege wa </s></f>"},{ID:42,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>angani huja na kukaa katika matawi yake.\" 
Akawaambia mfano mwingine: </s></f>"},{ID:43,Style:{Body:{FontSize:156}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>\"Ufalme wa mbingu umefanana na chachu aliyoitwaa </s></f>"},{ID:43,Style:{Body:{FontSize:196}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>mwanamke, akaichanganya na pishi tatu za unga, hata wote ukachacha.\"</s></f>"},{ID:44,Style:{Body:{FontSize:196}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Hayo yote Yesu aliyasema kwa makundi ya watu kwa mifano. </s></f>"},{ID:45,Style:{Body:{FontSize:180}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Pasipo mifano hakusema nao. Ilikuwa hivyo ili litimie lile lililosemwa </s></f>"},{ID:45,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>na nabii, \"Nitafumbua kinywa changu kwa mifano, 
nitatangaza yaliyofichika tangu mwanzo wa dunia.\"</s></f>"},{ID:46,Style:{Body:{FontSize:172}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Kisha Yesu akayaaga makundi ya watu, akaenda nyumbani. </s></f>"},{ID:47,Style:{Body:{FontSize:164}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Huko wafuasi wake wakamwendea, wakasema, \"Tufafanulie ule mfano </s></f>"},{ID:47,Style:{Body:{FontSize:164}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>wa magugu shambani.\" Akajibu akisema, </s></f>"},{ID:48,Style:{Body:{FontSize:164}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>\"Mtu apandaye mbegu njema ni Mwana wa Mtu. Shamba ni dunia. 
Mbegu njema ni wana </s></f>"},{ID:48,Style:{Body:{FontSize:164}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>wa ufalme. Magugu ni wana wa mwovu. Adui aliyeyapanda ni Shetani. </s></f>"},{ID:49,Style:{Body:{FontSize:180}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Mavuno ni mwisho wa dunia. Wavunaji ni malaika.</s></f>"},{ID:49,Style:{Body:{FontSize:180}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>Basi, kama magugu yanavyokusanywa na kuchomwa moto, </s></f>"},{ID:50,Style:{Body:{FontSize:188}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>ndivyo itakavyokuwa mwisho wa dunia. Mwana wa Mtu atawatuma </s></f>"},{ID:50,Style:{Body:{FontSize:188}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>malaika wake. Nao watakusanya katika ufalme wake makwazo yote, </s></f>"},{ID:51,Style:{Body:{FontSize:180}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>na watenda maovu na kuwatupa katika tanuli. humo </s></f>"},{ID:51,Style:{Body:{FontSize:254}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384>mtakuwamo kulia na kusaga meno.</s></f>"},{ID:52,Style:{Body:{FontSize:254}},
Text:"<s1384></s><fArial Black><s1384> Hapo waadilifu watang'aa kama jua katika ufalme wa Baba yao. 
Aliye na masikio, na asikie.''</s></f>"},{ID:53,Style:{Body:{FontSize:204}},
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1384>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f></b>"}],Style:{Body:{FontSize:276},Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA SITA MWAKA A"},{Guid:"WmjWFDsIIEqKvaD1PT75tA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>JUMAPILI YA PENTEKOSTE MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA	
Matendo ya Mitume 2:1-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Matendo ya Mitume</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku ya Pentekoste ilipowadia, wote walikuwapo mahali pamoja. </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mara uvumi ulitoka mbinguni kama upepo mkali,ukaijaza </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nyumba yote walimokaa. Na ndimi kama za moto zikawatokea, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>zikagawanyika na kutua kwa kila mmoja wao. Wote wakajazwa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Roho Mtakatifu, na wakaanza kusema lugha nyingine kama </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Roho Mtakatifu alivyowajalia kunena. Huko Yerusalemu </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>walikaa Wayahudi, watu wacha Mungu wa kila taifa lililoko </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>chini ya mbingu. Basi, uvumi huu ulipotukia, wengi walikutana, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakashikwa na mshangao kwa sababu kila mmoja wao </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliwasikia wanasema lugha yake mwenyewe. Wote walishtuka, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kwa mshangao waliuliza, \"Hao wote wanaosema si Wagalilaya? </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa namna gani kila mmoja wetu anaisikia lugha aliyozaliwa nayo? </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sisi Waparthi, Wamedia, Waelami, nasi tukaao Mesopotamia, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yudea, na Kapadokia, Ponto, na Asia, Firigia na Pamfilia, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Misri na wilaya za Libia kuelekea Kirene, pia wageni waliotoka Roma, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wayahudi na waongofu, Wakrete na Waarabu, sote tunawasikia </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakisema kwa lugha zetu, matendo makuu ya Mungu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana 
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA                          Zaburi 104: 1ab na 24ac, 29bc-30, 31 na 34 (K. 30)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Bwana, umtume roho wako na uufanye upya uso wa nchi.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu! Ee Bwana, Mungu wangu u mkuu sana!</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Bwana, jinsi gani zilivyo nyingi kazi zako! dunia imejaa viumbe vyako.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Bwana, umtume roho wako na uufanye upya uso wa nchi.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukiondoa pumzi yao, wanakufa, na kuyarudia mavumbi yao.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukimtuma roho wako wanaumbwa, na unafanya upya uso wa nchi. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Bwana, umtume roho wako na uufanye upya uso wa nchi.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Utukufu wa Bwana na udumu milele; Bwana na afurahie kazi zake!</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tafakari yangu na impendeze Mungu; nami nitafurahi katika Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Bwana, umtume roho wako na uufanye upya uso wa nchi </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
1 Akorintho 12:3-7,12-13</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Yohane 20:19-31</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jioni ya siku ile ya kwanza ya juma, alikuja Yesu, akasimama </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katikati, ingawa milango ya chumba walimokaa wafuasi </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ilikuwa imefungwa kwa kuwaogopa Wayahudi, akawaambia, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Amani iwe nanyi.” Baada ya maneno hayo, akawaonyesha </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mikono yake na ubavu wake. Wafuasi wakafurahi walipomwona </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana. Yesu akawaambia mara ya pili, “Amani iwe nanyi.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kama Baba alivyonituma mimi, nami nawatuma ninyi.”</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baada ya maneno hayo, akawapulizia, akawaambia, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Pokeeni Roho Mtakatifu. Wowote mtakaowaondolea dhambi,  </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wameondolewa, wowote mtakao wafungia dhambi, wamefungiwa.\"</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini Tomaso, aitwaye Pacha, mmoja wa wale Kumi na Wawili, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hakuwako pamoja nao alipokuja Yesu. Basi, wafuasi wengine </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakamwambia, \"Tumemwona Bwana. \"Yeye lakini akawajibu, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Nisipoona matundu ya misumari mikononi mwake, na kutia </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kidole changu sehemu za misumari, na kutia mkono wangu </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika ubavu wake, sisadiki hata kidogo.\" Baada ya siku nane, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wafuasi wake walikuwamo tena chumbani, na Tomaso pamoja nao.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akaja Yesu, ingawa milango ilikuwa imefungwa, akasimama </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katikati, akasema, \"Amani iwe nanyi.\" Kisha akamwambia </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tomaso, \"Tia kidole chako humu, tazama mikono yangu, lete mkono </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wako na kuutia katika ubavu wangu na usikose imani, bali uwe mwamini.\" </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tomaso akajibu akamwambia, \"Bwana wangu na Mungu wangu!\" </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akamwambia, \"Kwa kuwa umeniona, umesadiki? </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wenye heri wale wasioona, wakasadiki.\"  Sasa Yesu alifanya </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ishara nyingine nyingi mbele ya wafuasi wake zisizoandikwa </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika kitabu hiki. Lakini hizi zimeandikwa, mpate kusadiki </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya kuwa Yesu ni Masiya, Mwana wa Mungu, tena </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kusadiki mpate kuwa na uzima kwa jina lake.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana. 
(SIFA KWAKO EE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],
Text:"JUMAPILI YA PENTEKOSTE MWAKA A"},{Guid:"TeoApCmXKEyaHOY+wdevEw",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>MUCII MŪTHERU WA YESU, MARIA NA JOSEPH</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĪTHOMO KIA MBERE
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Sirach 3: 2-6; 12 - 14</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA KUUMA GITABU KIA SIRACH (”UGI WA JOSHUA BIN SIRA”) :</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nĩ akwenda ithe atīo nĩ ciana; na </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akūnengera nyina kihooto igūrū rīa ciana ciake.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Urīa ūtīaga ithe nĩ arehaga mawihia ; na ürīa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ükumagia nyina nĩ ta ürīa ünganagia mīthithū.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ürīa ütīaga ithe nĩ agakenio nĩ ciana ciake we mwene, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na rīrīa ahoyaga nī agwītikīrio.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Oria ūkumagia ithe nĩ akongererūo matukū make; ürīa </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>witikagia Mwathani nĩ agakenia nyina.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwana wakwa, teithia thoguo rīrīa akūrīte; ns ndūkae </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūmūiguithia üru kinya arī muoyo.O na angīta </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gītaranio, ümūiguīre tha na ndūkamūconokithie rīrīa </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee ürī na hinya. Amu tha gwa thoguo </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>itikariganīra, na igatarűo ithenya-inī rĩa thĩnjo ya mawīhia.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>THABURI YA GUCOKERŪO
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Thaburi128;1-2,3;4-5</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Gūkena-rī, nī mũndū o wothe witigagira Mwathani.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Gūkena-ri, nĩ mūndū o wothe mwitigīri Mwathani, o ūrīa ūgeraga njira ciake. </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kīra ūnogeire na moko maku-ri, wee ni ūrikirīaga; </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gūkena niwe ūrikenaga, na gutű</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ra ūtũ</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>re o na wega.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Gūkena-rī, nī mũndū o wothe wītigagīra Mwathani.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Mūtumia waku egũikara ta mūthabibū ürīa mūciari mūno o kūu nyūmba yaku thiinī :</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciana ciaku nacio ituike ta mĩtamaiyū ya mūmerano ithiūrūrūkirie metha yaku.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Gūkena-rī, nī mũndū o wothe wītigagīra Mwathani.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Onei, nĩ ta üguo mūndū arīrathimagwo, ūrīa mwītigīri Mwathani. </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani arokūrathima ari Sion, wonage wega wa </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jerusalemu matukū maku mothe ma gütū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ra muoyo.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Gūkena-rī, nī mũndū o wothe wītigagīra Mwathani.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGIRĪ
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Akolosai 3: 12 - 21</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA MARUA MA MUTHURE PAUL KURI ANDŪ A KOLOSI:</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariū a Ithe witū, kuona atī mūrī athure nĩ Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mügagītuika andū atheru mendetwo nīwe, wihumbei </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwīhumbīre wa ngoro ūrīa wa küiguanīra tha, na wa </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gütugana, na kwīnyihia, na kūhorera, o na</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gükirīrīria, mūgīkiranagīra na műkīohanagīra o mündű </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ürĩa üngī, angīkorūo nĩ harī mũndū mate</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tanīrie na ūrīa ūngī-ī; kīohanagīrei inyuene o ta ürīa </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nake aamuoheire inyuĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningī gūkīra maūndūmacio mothe-ri, gīagai na </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wendani, na nīguo wohanagia maūndū mothe hamwe</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīguo maagīrire kūna. Rekei thayű wa Kristü </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūteithüranage maūndũ mothe ngoro-inī cianyu; na</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīguo mwetīirūo mwathagwo nīguo, kuona atī műrí a </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwĩrī ümwe; ningī mügīage na ngatho.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rekei Ühoro wa Kristü üikarage üingīhīte műno thĩinĩ </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wanyu, ūkīmūūhīgagia na ūūgī wothe; na </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>műrutanage inyuí ene, mūgītaaranaga na thaburi, na </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nyīmbo cia Ngai, o na nyīmbo cia kūguna ma </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>muoyo wa andü, mükíinagīra Ngai mürī na Wega wake </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thĩinĩ wa ngoro cianyu. Na ningī atīrī : </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maūndū marīa mothe mūrikaga, műkíaria o na kana </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>műgīka ündū o ūrīkū-rí, mekagei na rīītwa rĩa </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani Yesu, mūgīcokagiria Ngai Ithe witű ngatho </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ündű wake, Inyuĩ atumia-rī , athīkagīrai </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>athuri anyu o ta ürīa kwagīríire andü arīa maikaraga </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thīĩi nī wa Mwathani. Na inyuī athuri -rī, endagai </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atumia anyu, na tigagai kümaküüma, O na inyuī ciana, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>iguagai aciari anyu maūũndū-inī mothe, nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ündũ üguo nīguo ükenagia Mwathani, Na inyuĩ maitherī, </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tigagai kürakaria ciana cianyu, műtigatūme igíe na kĩnyiria.</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RÜIMBO RŪA ALLELUYA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Akolosai 3: 15.16.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya, Alleluya. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thayū wa Kristū ūikaraçe ngoro-inī cianyu :</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mügambo wa Kristū üikarage äingīhīte müno thĩinĩ wanyu.</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĪTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mathayo 2: 13-15. 19 - 23</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĪCUNJĨ INJIRI THERU TA ŪRĪA YAN DĪKĪTWO NI MŪTHURE MATHAYO :</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amaji maainüka-rī, mũraika wa Ngai akiumirira Joseph </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kīroto-inĩ, akīmwīra: Ükīra, woe gakenge gaka </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nyina, mūürīre Misiri, mügaikare küu kinya hĩndí írĩa </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngakwīra műcoke; nĩ ündū Herode nī arīcaria </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gakenge gaka akoragithie. Nake agīgīükīra, akīoya </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gakenge na nyina ūtukū, magīthií Misiri ;</s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magītūūra kuo nginya hĩndī îra Herode aakuire, nĩ getha </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kiugo kīrīa kīoigirűo nĩ iwathani na kanua ka </s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>rathi kīhingio, rīrīa oigire ūű: Nĩ ndétire Mürű wakwa 
oime Misiri.</s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na atīrīrī, Herode aakua, mūraika wa Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akiumīrīria Joseph kīroto-inī o kūu Misiri, akīmwíra: </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ükīra, woe mwana na nyina műthiï bürūri wa Israeli, nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ündũ andū arīa mendaga kūüraga mwana nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makuīte. Nake agīükīra, akīoya mwana na nyina agīthií </s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>būrūri wa Israeli. Na rīrīa aaiguire atī Arkelao </s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīwe ürathámaka Judea ithenya rīa ithe Herode, </s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīītigīra gūthiĩ kuo; na aarīkia gükaanio nĩ Ngai na </s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kīroto, agīthīï ndwere cia Galilea, agīkinya itūūra </s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rīitagwo Nazareth, agītūüra kúo ni nĩ getha ūhoro </s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ühingio ürīa waaririo nī irori, atī nĩ agetagwo Mūnazari.</s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru Ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"OIP (2).jpg",Luminosity:-50}},
Text:"MUCII MŪTHERU WA YESU, MARIA NA JOSEPH
"},{Guid:"vD9WRvugf0ydafmUNs1sEw",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>FAMILIA TAKATIFU YA YESU, MARIA NA YOSEFU
MWAKA A</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Yoshua bin Sira 326. 12-14</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Yoshua bin Sira</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana alimtukuza baba kwa ajili ya watoto, na aliithibitisha haki</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya mama kwa ajili ya wana. Amheshimuye baba, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hufanya upatanisho wa dhambi. Naye amtukuzaye mama yake, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni kama mtu anayeweka akiba. Amheshimuye baba atafurahishwa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na watoto wake, na katika siku ya sala yake atasikilizwa.
Amtukuzaye baba atapata maisha marefu; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye anayemti Bwana atamstarehesha mama yake. Mtoto, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umsaidie baba yako katika uzee wake; wala usimhuzunishe katika maisha yake.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hata akipungukiwa na ufahamu, umvumilie kwa upole; </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala usimdharau uwapo katika nguvu yako yote. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana wema kwa baba hautasahauliwa, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na utakusaidia kukupatia msamaha wa dhambi.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Zaburi 128: 1-2, 3, 45 (K. )</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Heri kila mtu amchaye Bwana, aendaye katika njia zake.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Heri kila mtu amchaye Bwana,aendaye katika njia zake.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakika utakula matunda ya kazi ya mikono yako;
utabarikiwa na kupata fanaka. K.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Heri kila mtu amchaye Bwana, aendaye katika njia zake.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mkeo atakuwa kama mzabibu uzaao
ndani ya nyumba yako,</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wanao kama machipukizi ya mizeituni,
wakizunguka meza yako. K.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Heri kila mtu amchaye Bwana, aendaye katika njia zake.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndivyo atakavyobarikiwa
yule amchaye Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana na akubariki toka Sioni,
na uione fanaka ya Yerusalemu,
siku zote za maisha yako.K.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Heri kila mtu amchaye Bwana, aendaye katika njia zake.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Wakolosai 3:12-211</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakolosai</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Kama wateule wa Mungu, watakatifu na wapenzi</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wake, jivikeni moyo wa huruma, wema, unyenyekevu, upole na</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>subira. Mvumiliane na msameheane, na kama mmoja ana lalamiko</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>dhidi ya mwenzake, basi kama Bwana alivyowasameheni, nanyi
mfanye vivyo hivyo.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zaidi ya hayo yote, ongezeni upendo ambao ndio kifungo cha</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ukamilifu. Na acheni amani ya Kristo itawale mioyoni mwenu,</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maana kwa ajili yake mmeitwa kuwa viungo vya mwili mmoja.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muwe na shukrani. Neno la Kristo likae ndani yenu kwa wingi,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika kufundishana kwa hekima na kuhimizana wenyewe na katika</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>zaburi na nyimbo na tenzi za kiroho, mkiimba kwa shukrani kwa
Bwana. </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yoyote mfanyayo kwa maneno au matendo, yafanyeni kwa</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>jina la Bwana Yesu mkimshukuru Mungu Baba kwa njia yake yeye.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Enyi akina mama, watiini waume zenu kama ipasavyo katika Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Enyi waume, wapendeni wake zenu, msiwe na uchungu dhidi yao.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Enyi watoto, watiini wazazi wenu katika yote, kwani hiyo inapendeza
kwa Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Enyi akina baba, msiwachokoze watoto wenu wasije wakakata tamaa.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Wakolosai 3:15a.16a</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Amani ya Kristo itawale mioyoni mwenu;
neno la Kristo likae ndani yenu kwa wingi..</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mathayo 2:13-15, 19 23</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili akatifu ilivyoandikwa na Mathayo</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Walipoondoka Mamajusi, tazama, malaika wa Bwana alimtokea</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yosefu katika ndoto, akisema, “Amka, umtwae mtoto mchanga</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mama yake, ukimbilie Misri. Kaa huko mpaka nitakaposema nawe.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana Herode ataka kumtafuta mtoto mchanga amwangamize.”</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alipoamka, alimtwaa mtoto na mama yake usiku, akaondoka</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwenda Misri. Akakaa huko mpaka kifo cha Herode.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hivyo neno alilosema Bwana kwa njia ya nabii likatimia,</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwamba, Nalimwita mwanangu kutoka Misri.”.</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi Herode alipokufa, tazama, malaika wa Bwana akamtokea</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yosefu katika ndoto huko Misri. Akasema, “Amka, umtwae mtoto</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mama yake, uende katika nchi ya Israeli, kwa maana waliotafuta</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uhai wa mtoto wamefariki.”</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, akaamka, akamtwaa mtoto na mama yake, akaenda katika nchi
ya Israeli.</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aliposikia ya kuwa Arkelao anatawala Yudea mahali pa baba yake</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Herode, aliogopa kwenda huko. Akionywa tena na Mungu katika</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndoto, akaelekea pande za Galilaya.</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Huko akakaa katika mji uitwao Nazareti kusudi litimie neno</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Iililosemwa na manabii: Ataitwa Mnazareti.”</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_ddf7796b.jpg"}},
Text:"FAMILIA TAKATIFU YA YESU, MARIA NA YOSEFU
MWAKA A
"},{Guid:"9iM/73kHuUaRsAAvdbtvUw",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.59.51_2a32560f.jpg"}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>UBATITHU WA YESU KRISTU MWAKA A</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Isaia 42:1-4,6-7</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>	 
Mwathani  ekuuga ũũ: ĩno nĩyo ndungata yakwa ĩrĩa ndiirĩrĩire; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩyo ĩrĩa ndĩĩthurĩire, na nĩyo ĩkenagia ngoro yakwa: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ndĩmĩikũrũkĩirie muoyo wakwa ũkamĩhuba, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩyo ĩkarehithĩrie ndũrĩrĩ cira wa kĩhooto.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndĩkaanĩrĩra, o na kana ĩhaicie kayũ kayo na igũrũ,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> o na kana ĩtũme mũgambo wayo ũigwo njĩra-inĩ.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kamũrangi kagondoku ndĩgakoina, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana rũtambĩ rũa ũguta rũgĩtoga ĩrũhorie.
  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gũtua ĩgatuanagĩra cira wa ma. Ndĩkahwererekera, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana yume tha, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ĩgakorũo ĩtũmĩte gũkũ thĩ kũgĩe cira wa kĩhooto; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andũ arĩa matũũraga ithama-inĩ magaikaraga metereire watho wayo. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niĩ Mwathani-rĩ, nĩ niĩ ngwĩtĩte o ta ũrĩa nyonaga kwerekeire, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ ngakũnyita guoko na  ngũmenyagĩrĩre,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ngũheane nĩ getha ũtuĩke wa kũrĩkanĩra kĩrĩkanĩro na andũ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ũtuĩke ũtheri wa gũtherera andũ a ndũrĩrĩ;</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> o na ningĩ nĩ getha ũhingũrage maitho marĩa matumumu, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao andũ arĩa mohetwo ũmarutage kĩoho-inĩ,  </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nao arĩa maikarĩte nduma-inĩ-rĩ,
ũmarutage korokoro-inĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Thaburi 29: 1-2;3-4;8-10</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rahai Mwathani, inyuĩ ariũ a Mũrungu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na e hinya;</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> rahai Mwathani mũkĩgane riri wa rĩĩtwa rĩake; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thathaiyai Mwathani mwĩgemetie na ũgemu ũrĩa wa ũtheru.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ kũgamba ũragamba na kũu iria-inĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũrungu, ũcio wĩ riri, nĩ hĩndĩ egũkĩruruma,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> o we Mwathani akaruruma kũu igũrũ rĩa maaĩ maingĩ.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũgambo wa Mwathani wĩna hinya; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ mũkaru o gũkara.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũgambo wa Mwathani nĩ ũthingithagia werũ; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũgatũma mĩtitũ ĩhũrũrũke o gũthera; Mwathani-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o hingo ĩrĩa ya Mũiyũro wa Maaĩ; ĩĩ-ni, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani aikaraga  ho e mũthamaki wa mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Ũkumio na gĩtĩo kwa rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</k></c></s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200>Atumwo  10:34-38</c></s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Peter agĩitĩka kwaria akiuga atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ti-itherũ ndĩ kuona atĩ Ngai ndatĩagĩra andũ maũthĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no thĩinĩ wa ndũrĩrĩ ciothe mũndũ ũrĩa ũmwĩtigagĩra </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ageka maũndũ ma ũthingu nĩ etĩkagĩrũo nĩwe. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Atĩrĩrĩ: Ũhoro ũrĩa aarekeirie ciana cia Israeli, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ũrĩa wa kũhunjanĩria ndeto njega cia thayũ ũrĩa wonekaga na Yesu Kristũ,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nake nĩwe Mwathani wa guothe.  Ũhoro ũcio-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>inyuĩ nĩ mũũĩ, naguo nĩguo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wahunjanĩirio Judea guothe wambĩrĩirio  o Galilea,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> thutha wa rĩrĩa John aaheanire ũhoro wa atĩ andũ mabatithio.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naguo nĩ wa Yesu wa Nazareth,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> ũrĩa Ngai aamũitĩrĩirie Muoyo Mũtheru o na hinya; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake agĩcamba agĩĩkaga maũndũ mega, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na akĩhonagia andũ arĩa othe maatũire manyariragwo nĩ mũcukani: </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gũkorũo Ngai aarĩ hamwe nake.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Marko 9,7 </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>		
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya. Alleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thĩinĩ wa itu gũkiuma mũgambo wa Ithe akiuga atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Ũyũ nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa, nyendete mũno: mũiguagei”.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluia</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĪTHOMO KĪA INJIRI
Mathayo 3: 13- 17</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĪCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŪRIA YANDIKĪTWO NI MŪTHURE MATHAYO :</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndī īo, Yesu nī oimire Galilea, agithií Jordano kürī John, akabatithio nīwe. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake John nĩ endaga kūmūgiria, akīmūūria : </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nií-rĩ, nĩ njagīrīirűo nĩ kūbatithio nīwe, nawe ügūüka kūrī niī, atia ?</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akīmūcokeria akīmwīra atīrĩ: Njitikīria rīu, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondū üguo nīguo twagiríirūo nī kūhingia
maūndū mothe marīa merekanīííire na ūthingu, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndī īo akīmwītikīria. Nake Yesu aarikia kübatithio, akiumīra o rīmwe maaī - inī, na atĩrīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Igūrű rikīhingüka, akīona muoyo wa Ngai agīikūrüka
ta ndutura, akīümba igūrű rĩake. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na atīrirī, mūgambo ūkiuma lgūrū, ükiuga:  úyú nīwe Mürū wakwa nyendete mūno, nĩ ngenaga ní ündű wake.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.59.51_2a32560f.jpg"}},
Text:"KIUMIA GIA THUTHA WA EPIPHANIA UBATITHU WA YESU KRISTU
 MWAKA A"},{Guid:"RcTmsgn3bkeON+bnJDyjVw",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>UBATIZO WA BWANA YESU MWAKA A</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
Isaya 42:1-4,6-7</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana asema hivi:
\"Huyu ndiye mtumishi wangu ninayemtegemeza, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mteule wangu,
moyo wangu unapendezwa naye.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nimeweka roho yangu juu yake;
atawajulisha mataifa hukumnu ya haki.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hatalia, wala hatapaza sauti:
wala hatapiga kelele katika njia za miji.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hatavunja mwanzi uliokunjika,
hatazima utambi unaozimika;</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bali ataleta haki kwa uaminifu.
Hatazimia wala hatakata tamaa,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mpaka atakapoweka hukumu duniani,
na nchi za pwani zitangojea mafundisho yake.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi, Bwana, nimekuita kwa ajili ya haki,
nimekushika mkono;</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nimekuumba, nikakuweka kuwa agano la taifa,
na mwanga wa mataifa.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ii kuwafumbua vipofu macho,
ili kuwaondosha vifungoni waliofungwa,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kuwaondosha gerezani wale wanaokaa gizani.\"</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKZANA 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Zaburi 29: la na 2, 3ac 4, 3b na 9b-10 (K. 11b</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K.</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000> Bwana atawabariki watu wake kwa amani!</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Mpeni Bwana, enyi wana wa Mungu,
mpeni Bwana sifa na enzi;</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mpeni Bwana utukufu wa jina lake,
mwangukieni Bwana aking'ara kwa utakatifu! K.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Bwana atawabariki watu wake kwa amani!</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Sauti ya Bwana i juu ya maji;
Bwana ananguruma juu ya maji mengi.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sauti ya Bwana ina nguvu sana;
sauti ya Bwana ni ya fahari. K.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Bwana atawabariki watu wake kwa amani!</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Bwana wa huruma ananguruma.
Hekaluni mwake wote husema, \"Utukufu!\"</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ameketi kama mfalme juu ya gharika!
Bwana ametawazwa kama mfalme wa milele! K.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Bwana atawabariki watu wake kwa amani!</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Matendo ya Mitume 10:34-38</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Matendo ya Mitume</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Petro alifumbua kinywa, akasema, \"Hakika, sasa nimeng'amua ya kuwa Mungu hana ubaguzi.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bali, katika kila taifa, mtu yeyote mwenye kumcha yeye na kutenda yaliyo haki hukubaliwa naye. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu aliwapelekea wana wa Israeli neno lake,</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tena ni hao walioletewa na Yesu Kristo habari njema ya amani,</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni huyu Yesu Kristo aliye Bwana wa wote. Mmejua yaliyotukia katika Uyahudi wote kuanzia Galilaya,</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>baada ya ubatizo aliouhubiri Yohane, jinsi Mungu alivyompaka mafuta, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu wa Nazareti kwa Roho Mtakatifu na nguvu.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na jinsi alivyozunguka katika nchi yote akitenda mema na kuwaponya wote walioonewa na Shetani, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana Mungu
alikuwa pamoja naye.\"</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Marko 9:7</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Wingu lilitokea,na sauti ya Baba ikatokea mbinguni ikisema,
Huyu ni Mwanangu mpendwa, msikilizeni yeye.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mathayo 3:13-17</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Mathayo</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Yesu alitoka Galilaya, akafika Yordani kwa Yohane abatizwe naye. </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini Yohane alitaka kumzuia akisema, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Mimi nahitaji kubatizwa na wewe, nawe unakuja kwangu?\"
Yesu akajibu, akamwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Acha iwe hivyo kwa sasa, kwa maana
ndivyo yatupasa kutimiza haki yote.\" </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akamkubalia alivyosema.
Baada ya kubatizwa, </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akatoka mara majini.
Na tazama, mbingu zikafunguka.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akamwona Roho wa Mungu akimshukia kwa mfano wa njiwa.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tazama, pale pale sauti ikatoka mbinguni ikisema,
\"Huyu ni Mwanangu mpendwa, anipendezaye.\"</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.59.51_2a32560f.jpg",Luminosity:-35}},
