Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Isaya 49 : 3.5-6</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ameniambia:
Wewe ni mtumishi wangu, ee Israeli, katika wewe nítatukuzwa.\"</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na sasa Bwana asema,
yeye aliyenitunga tangu tumboni niwe mtumishi wake,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili nimrudishie Yakobo, na kukusanya Israeli mbele yake;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nami nimepata heshima machoni pa Bwana
na Mungu wangu amekuwa nguvu yangu!</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amesema: \"Ni jambo dogo wewe kuwa mtumishi wangu,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili kuyainua makabila ya Yakobo,
na kuwarudisha wale waliobaki katika Israeli;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nimekuweka kuwa mwanga wa mataifa,
ili wokovu wangu uenee mpaka miisho ya dunia.\"</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Zaburi 40:2 na 4ab, 7-8a, 8b-9, 10 (K. &a na 9a)</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Tazama, nimnekuja kuyatimiza mapenzi yako, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nalimngojea Bwana kwa subira;
akanielekea na kukisikia kilio changu,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akaweka wimbo mpya kinywani mwangu,
sifa za Mungu wetu. K.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Tazama, nimnekuja kuyatimiza mapenzi yako, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hukupenda sadaka wala matoleo;
ila masikio wazi kwa kutii;</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hukutaka dhabihu za kuteketeza wala sadaka za dhambi: \"Tazama, nimekuja.\" K.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Tazama, nimnekuja kuyatimiza mapenzi yako, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hapo nilisema,
Katika gombo la chuo nimeandikiwa amri zako.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Napenda kutimiza mapenzi yako,
ee Mungu wangu, sheria yako imo mnoyoni mwangu! K.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Tazama, nimnekuja kuyatimiza mapenzi yako, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ninatangaza habari za haki yako
katika mkutano mkubwa;</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala sikuzuia midomo yangu,
ee Bwana, wewe wajua. K.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Tazama, nimekuja kuyatimiza mapenzi yako, ee Bwana</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>1 Wakorintho 1:1-3</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwanzo wa barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo
kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi Paulo,
kwa jina la Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo,</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>niliyeitwa kwa kusudio la Mungu kuwa mtume wa Yesu Kristo,</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ndugu Sostenesi tunapeleka salamu, kwa Kanisa la Mungu lililoko Korintho, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani kwa waliotakaswa katika Kristo Yesu
na kuitwa kuwa watakatifu </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>pamoja na wote wanaosali
kila mahali wanapoishi na kwetu pia.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neema na amani kutoka kwa Mungu Baba yetu, na kwa Bwana Yesu Kristo ziwe nanyi.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Yohane 1:14a, 12a</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>.</k></s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Neno alifanyika mwili, akakaa kwetu,
wote waliompokea aliwapa uwezo
wa kuwa watoto wa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W.</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000> Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Yohane 1:29-34</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule:
Yohane alimwona Yesu anakuja kwake, akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tazameni, Mwanakondoo wa Mungu
aondoaye dhambi za ulimwengu.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Huyu ndiye niliyemtaja niliposema,
'Anakuja nyuma yangu mtu aliyekuwa kabla yangu,</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana yeye alikuwako kwanza.'</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sikumjua, lakini kusudi ajulikane katika Israeli,
mimi nimekuja kubatiza kwa maji.\"</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yohane alitoa pia ushuhuda huu,
Nimemwona Roho akishuka kama njiwa
kutoka mbinguni na kukaa juu yake.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi sikumjua,
lakini yeye aliyenituma kubatiza kwa maji aliniambia,</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yeye ambaye utamwona Roho anamshukia na kubaki juu yake.,</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huyo ndiye abatizaye kwa Roho Mtakatifu.
Nami nimeona, tena nimeshuhudia,</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwamba huyu ni Mwana wa Mungu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_ddf7796b.jpg"}},
