Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>KIUMIA KIA IGIRÍ KĨA MWAKA A</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Isaia 49 : 3.5-6</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GÜTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RiA MŪRA THI ISAIA :</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani agīgīcoka akīnjīra atīrĩ: Wee nīwe ndungata yakwa, Israeli, nĩ thĩinĩ waku ndīigoocagwo .</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani, o we ürīa wanyümbire ndī o nda, nĩ getha nduike ndungata ya kühūndūra Jakobu ndīmūcokie harī we, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ya gūcokereria lsraeli harī we, - nĩ gükorūo niĩ ndĩ mūtīku ngīonwo nī Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nake Ngai wakwa nĩwe ūtuikíte hinya wakwa rī, - ücio ekuuga üű : </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ti-itherü ūnd üyū ní mũhüth</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>, atĩ wee ütuike ndungata</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> yakwa nīguo ütūme andũ a mūhīriga wa Jakobu maarahūrūo, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ona t</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> ücokererie matigari ma andū a Israeli. Ürĩa ngūkuongerera-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ atī ūtuike ūtheri wa gūthe andū a ndūrīrī, nīguo ūtuîke wa gūkinyia űhoro wakwa wa kūhonokania ituri-inī cia thĩ ciothe .</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŪCOKERŪO
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Thaburi 40:1 na 3a; 6-7a; 76-8; 9</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Niĩ ndī gūūka, Mwathani, gwíka wendi waku.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Gwíterera ndetereire Mwathani o ngiriririe, nake agikiíhůgürira akīnjerekera, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aginikīra kūigua kiriro gīakwa. Agīgiikira kanua gwakwa rűimbo rūerū, o rüa ūgooci, ngoocage Ngai witŭ naruo.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Niĩ ndī gūūka, Mwathani, gwíka wendi waku.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2. Wee-rī, ti magongona na mahaki ūkenagira; ūndū wikīte, ni kwega ūnjegete matū: mahaki ma gucinwo,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ma kūrutwo ni ũndū wa mehia-ri, timo witītie. Hindi io ngīkiuga atīri: Nií üyū,ndí gūüka .</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA :</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000> Niĩ ndī gūūka, Mwathani, gwíka wendi waku.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Thiini wa ibuku, o rīo ria gikūnjo, ühoro wakwa nīho wandīkītwo : </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niĩ ngenagio no gwika üria wendaga, wee Ngai wakwa; ri-ni, kīrīra gīaku kūrī o ngoro-inī yakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA :</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000> Niĩ ndī gūūka, Mwathani, gwíka wendi waku.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4. Uhoro mwega, ūria wa ūthingu, nì ndīwanirire ndi kīüngano-inī kirīa kīnene; </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mīromo yakwa ndiri ndamigiririria: wee, Mwathani, ni tũi üguo .</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA :</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000> Niĩ ndī gūūka, Mwathani, gwíka wendi waku.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>1 Akorintho 1: 1-3</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA MARŪA MA MÜTHURE PAUL KURÍ ANDŪ A KORINTHO MARĪA MA MBERE :</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ nií Paulo, o nií ndetirūo na kwenda kwa Ngai nduīke mūtümwo wa Yesu Kristű, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ng</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>tüma ngeithi ici, türí na Sostene, mürű wa Ithe witü; </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>twatümĩra kanitha wa Ngai üría ürí Korintho, o inyuí arīa mwamūrītwo ní gūīikara thīinī wa Kristű Yesu,</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mügetwo műtuike andű aaműre; nĩ inyuī twatūmīra mwī hamwe </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na andū othe a kündū guothe arīa makayagira riīitwa rĩa Mwathani witū Yesu Kristű,</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we Mwathani wao o na witū,Atīrīrī : mürogīa na Wega, o na thayũ, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciumīte kwī Ngai Ithe witű na Mwathani Yesu Kristū .</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŪĪMBO RŪA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>John 1 : 29- 34</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya, Alleluya. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uge agigītuīka mündũ na agītūürania na ithuĩ. Aria othe maamwītikīrire,acio akīmahotithia gütuika ciana cia Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya .</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>John 1: 14. 12</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GICUNJÍ KIA INJIRI THERU TA ÜRĪA YANDIKITWO NĪ MŪTHURE JOHN</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hīndī íyo, John akīona Yesu agiüka arorete kūrī we, akiuga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Onei Gatūrüme ka Ngai, karīa gag</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>twara mehia ma kirīndī. </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Üyū nowe ndoigire, atī: Thutha wakwa nī gügūūka mũndū ūgiĩte mbere yakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gükorűo aarī kuo mbere yakwa. Na ndiamū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>í o na niï;</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Índī nīguo aguūkīre Israeli, nĩKīo ndokire ngībatithagia andū na maaī. </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O nake John akīheana űira, akiuga : Nĩ nyonete Muoyo agīikürūka akiuma lgürű ahaana ta ndutura,</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> agīikara igūrű rīake. Na ndiakīmūuí o na niŭ; Índī üria
wandekirie ngabatithanie na maaī, </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we nĩ aanjīrire atīrī : Ürīa ükona Muoyo agīikūrūkírīra agaikara igürű rīake, </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ücio nīwe übatithanagia na Muoyo Mütheru. Na nĩ nyonete na ngoimbūra atī ūyũ nowe Mürű wa Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani .</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_ddf7796b.jpg"}},
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IGIRÍ KĨA MWAKA A
"},{Guid:"2j51pfgcqU6/2VsdinMEvg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
Isaia 22: 19-23</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GÜTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RiA MÜRATHI ISAIA</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani akimenyithia Shebna üü : Atiriri, ngagütugutania urutwo wira-ini waku, uguthwo uru two handü haku hau hatüügiru .</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Na ni gügakinya atiri, müthenya ücio,ati ni ngeta ndungata yakwa Eliakim wa Hilikia, ndimühumbe nguo yaku iria ndaya, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndimühotore mwihotoro waku, na wira wa ku wa gwathana ndiwikire moko-ini make ; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ücio niwe ügatuika ta ithe wa andü aria matüüraga Jerusalemu, na wa andü a nyümba ya Juda. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kihingüro kia nyümba ya Davide-ri, ngakiigirira kiande - ini giake, atuike mühingüraniri, na gütigie mühinganiriria ; na ahinganagiririe na gütigie mühinguraniri o na atü;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na ndimuoherere handü harümu aikare ho ta mücumari ühüriirüo handü, atuike ogiti  gia üthamaki kii riri thiini wa nyümba ya ithe.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani .</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GÜCOKERÜO
Thaburi 138: 1-2a; 2b-3; 6 na 8</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : </s></f><i><fArial Black><s2769>Küringana na ütugi waku, Mwathani, ndümütiganiria</s></f></i><fArial Black><s2769>.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ni ngügücokeria ngatho na ngoro yakwa yothe, ngüküinira ngukugoocaga ngai ciothe iri o ho. Ngüinamirira njerekeire hekarü yaku theru.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<i><fArial Black><s2769>Küringana na ütugi waku, Mwathani, ndümütiganiria.</s></f></i>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Njokerie ritwa riaku ngatho ni ündü wa ütugi waku, na tondü wa wihokeku waku o naguo, amu nikünenehia ünenehetie uuge waku küri maündü maria mangi ma ritwa riaku mothe.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Müthio üria ndetanire, wee ni wanyamukiirie; ni wanyümiriirie ni künjikira
 hinya ngoro.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<i><fArial Black><s2769>Küringana na ütugi waku, Mwathani, ndümütiganiria.</s></f></i>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ni hindü, o na gwatuika Mwathani e igürü müno, ni aroraga mündü mühoreri;indi, uria mwitüügiria, akamümenyera o küraya. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani, maündü makwa ni akamakindira: ütugi waku, Mwathani, ni wa tene na tene; wira wa moko maku-ri, ndükanaütiganirie.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<i><fArial Black><s2769>Küringana na ütugi waku, Mwathani, ndümütiganiria</s></f></i><fArial Black><s2769>.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GiTHOMO KiA IGIRT	
Aroma 11 : 33-36</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GÜTHOMA MARÜA MA MÜTHURE PAUL KÜRi ANDÜ A ROMA</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>i üügi wa Ngai, o naguo umenyi wake-ri, matikiri maingi na mariku ! Matuiro make, kai matingica rika gitümi kiamo;</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> migendere yake nayo, kai ndingituirika -i ! Amu ni mündü ürikü Wanamenya meciria ma Mwathani ? kana ni ürikü wanatuika wa ndundu yake ? Kana riri, nü wanaamba kü.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> mühe kindü, nake akarihwo kindü kiu ? Amu-ri, maündü mothe no hari we moimire,na gütüürio matüüragio no we,</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na no küri we merekeire. Nake arogoocagwo tene na tene. Ni gutuike guo.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RÜiMBO RüA INJIRI	
Mathayo 16, 18
Alleluya, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Wee niwe Petro, na igürü ria ndümba ya ihiga riri ni ngaaka Kanitha wakwa, na ihingo cia kwa ngoma itikaütoria.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Alleluya .</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GiTHOMO KIA INJIRI	Mathayo 16; 13-20</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GiCUNJi KIA INJIRI THERU TA ÜRiA YANDiKiTWO Ni MÜTHURE MATHAYO</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi iyo Yesu aakinya bürüri-ini wa Cesarea wa Filippo, akiüria arutwo ake atiri : Andü moigaga ati Mürü wa mündü nüü? </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao makiuga atiri: Amwe moigaga ati niwe John Mübatithania; na amwe makoiga niwe Elia ; na angi makoiga niwe Jeremia, kana ümwe waarathi.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Nake akimoria : Inyui na inyui muugaga ni nii üü? Nake Simone Petro akimücokeria akimwira atiri: Wee, niwe Kristu, Mürü wa Ngai üria wi muoyo.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Nake Yesu akimücokeria akimwira : Gükena-ri, niwe Simone, mürü wa Jona : ni ündü ti mündü wi mwiri na thakame üküguüriirie üguo, no ni Awa üria wi igüru.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Na ningükwira atiri. Wee niwe Petro, o na igürü ria ndümba ya ihiga riri ni ngaaka Kanitha wakwa: o na ihingo cia kwa ngoma itikaütoria.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ni ngakühe ihingüro cia üthamaki wa lgürü : na kiria o giothe ükoha gükü thi ni gikohwo lgürü; na kiria o giothe ükohora gükü thi, ni gikohorüo Igürü.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Hindi io agikaania arutwo ake matikae kwira mündü o na ümwe ati niwe Kristü .</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJIRI YA MWATHANI</s></f>"}],
Text:"kiumia kia mirongo iri na kimwe mwaka A"}],IsCompressed:0,Guid:"fQAcKhkjV0qv8ZrNEJVoMA",
Text:"MATHOMO MA MWAKA A"}